    "Id": "223454",
    "ThreadId": "65228",
    "Html": "<p>In your CellEditingTemplate you need to set a two way binding of the SelectedItem of the ComboBox to the Car property.&nbsp; You also need to set IsSychronizedWithCurrentItem=&rsquo;false&rsquo; on the &lt;ComboBox /&gt; inside the &lt;DataGridTemplateColumn /&gt;.</p>",
